IMAPAccount linode
# Address to connect to
Host emilyshepherd.me
User emily
PassCmd "cat ~/Private/conf/email"
# Use SSL
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore personal
Account linode

MaildirStore local
Path ~/Private/mail/
Inbox ~/Private/mail/INBOX
Flatten .

Channel main
Master :personal:
Slave :local:
Patterns % ML/*/* !ML
Create Both
SyncState *
Expunge Both
